getLoginTimesPerMemberWithoutZeros

public java.util.List<Pair<User,java.lang.Number>> getLoginTimesPerMemberWithoutZeros()
gets a list with Pairs, where the first element of each pair is the member id, and the second element is the number of times that member logged in. Same as getLoginTimesPerMember except that this list has the zero results skipped, as needed by the top ten.

a list with member id's and login times.
